high_descs: turn right to face the kitchen counter
grab the lettuce off of the kitchen counter
turn around and walk to the end of the room, then turn left to face the fridge
place the lettuce inside of the fridge to cool, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the kitchen table on your right
place the lettuce down on the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place cooled lettuce down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn right and go to the counter, near the sink.
Pick up the cabbage on the counter.
Turn around, go straight, and then turn left to go to the fridge.
Chill the cabbage in the fridge.
Turn left, go straight, then turn right to face the table next to the fridge.
Place the cabbage on the table, to the left of the plate.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled cabbage on the table.

high_descs: pick up the pawpaw on the pavement
turn around  and head towards the fridge
put the pawpaw inside the fridge and allow it to cool then take it out
turn left and move towards the table
place the pawpaw on the table
anns.task_desc: place a cold pawpaw on the table
